name: 02.AlIgN
description:
Video & Art by Gino, 9/21.

This piece is a gift to the early adopters of my work. These early works represent the first steps in an important phase in my life while revisiting over a decade of my work asking "so what?" Your support allows me to continue this journey as a visual artist.

This is just the beginning-- THANK YOU!  Your support means more to me than you could possibly know.
